trans-unit.source: Use the `AssignCulture` element in your project file to create and execute this task.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av `AssignCulture` elementet i prosjektfilen til å opprette og kjøre denne oppgaven.

trans-unit.source: For usage and parameter information, see [AssignCulture Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For bruk og parametere informasjon, se [AssignCulture oppgaven](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*> with a `Culture` metadata entry added to each item.
trans-unit.target: Henter en liste over <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*>med en `Culture` metadata oppføring legges til i hvert element.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*>

trans-unit.source: If the incoming item from the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files%2A> property already contains a `Culture` metadata entry, the original metadata entry is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis innkommende element fra den <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files%2A>egenskapen inneholder allerede en `Culture` metadata post, den opprinnelige metadata brukes.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files%2A>

trans-unit.source: The task only assigns a `Culture` metadata entry if the file name contains a valid culture identifier.
trans-unit.target: Oppgaven bare tilordner en `Culture` metadata posten Hvis filnavnet inneholder en gyldig kultur-identifikator.

trans-unit.source: The culture identifier must be between the last two dots in the filename.
trans-unit.target: Kultur-IDen må være mellom to prikker i filnavnet.

trans-unit.source: The list of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*>, with a `Culture` metadata entry added to each item.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a list of files with embedded culture names to assign a culture to.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en liste over filer med innebygde kulturen navn til å tilordne en kultur til.
